                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7063" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0218</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8994 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大鹏一日同飞起，扶摇直上九万里—格力电器混合所有制改革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Dapeng flies together on the same day and soars up to 90000 miles - the road of mixed ownership reform of Gree Electric Appliance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张劲松，王萌萌，刘林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">珠海格力电器股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">格力电器；混合所有制改革；股权结构；财务绩效</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gree Electric Appliance;Mixed ownership reform;ownership structure;Financial performance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自中共中央十八届三中全会以来，党中央提出积极发展混合所有制经济。十九大报告进一步强调深化国有企业改革，逐步加大改革力度。混改政策的接连落地进一步推动了“双百行动”的进行与2020年开展的“三年行动方案”的落实，加快了混合所有制的改革步伐。在考察企业“一企一策”混合所有制改革路径时，结合混合企业改革现状，通过重组、引入战略投资者、基金引入、上市、员工参与等方式进行改革创新。越来越多的案例证明了对混改路径的正确选择是决定混改成功与否的关键。目前，大多数实施混改的公司都实现了公司价值的提升，这表明混改是国有企业在市场化环境下发展的必然选择。然而，许多公司仍存在混改路径选择错误、混改方案实施不彻底等问题。格力电器作为混改成功企业的代表具有一定分析价值，因此，本案例选择以董明珠参与格力电器混改为主线，讨论格力电器混改原因、混改过程、混改后格力电器取得的成效以及存在的不足，旨在为其他国企混改提供借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the Third Plenary Session of the 18th CPC Central Committee, the CPC Central Committee has proposed to actively develop the mixed ownership economy. The report of the 19th National Congress further emphasized deepening the reform of state-owned enterprises and gradually increasing the reform efforts. The successive implementation of the mixed ownership reform policy further promoted the implementation of the &quot;Double Hundred Action&quot; and the &quot;Three Year Action Plan&quot; in 2020, and accelerated the reform of mixed ownership. When reviewing the &quot;one enterprise, one policy&quot; mixed ownership reform path of enterprises, and considering the current situation of mixed enterprise reform, reform and innovation are carried out through restructuring, introducing strategic investors, introducing funds, listing, employee participation, etc. More and more cases have proved that the correct choice of mixed transformation path is the key to the success of mixed transformation. At present, most of the companies implementing the mixed transformation have realized the improvement of company value, which indicates that the mixed transformation is an inevitable choice for the development of state-owned enterprises in the market-oriented environment. However, many companies still have problems such as wrong choice of mixed transformation path, incomplete implementation of mixed transformation scheme, etc. Gree Electric has certain analytical value as a representative of a successful enterprise in the mixed transformation. Therefore, Dong Mingzhu&#39;s participation in the mixed transformation of Gree Electric is chosen as the main line in this case to discuss the reasons for the mixed transformation of Gree Electric, the process of the mixed transformation, the achievements and shortcomings of Gree Electric after the mixed transformation, so as to provide reference for other state-owned enterprises in the mixed transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《公司战略分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国企混改的动因及驱动力；国企混改的一般模式；国企混改前后股权结构变化以及相关指标计算；格力电器混改成功的经验；格力电器混改存在的不足之处</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
